summary: THE TRAILER (UNPOWERED VEHICLE) I RENTED FROM BUDGET RENTAL PUT MY SAFETY AT RISK. I WAS GIVEN UNSAFE EQUIPMENT THAT JEOPARDIZED MY SAFETY.
